item.title: How do i make ::master commands on a 508!

item.description:
@r34p4g3pk wrote:

Why don’t you just download rubiks 508, so when you click the hay you get all 99’s, or make npcs. You don’t need ""master on a 508 it kinda ruins it, but yeah i would beleive it’s near the commands, so just search a command like ::bh, search “bh,” in client.java and copy that to make a ::master command, but you would need to let it give you a 99 stat aswell, i’m not so into 508’s but i think that’s how you do it.
